seo: Quicklancer,SQL注入漏洞,高危漏洞,插件检测
seo_en: Quicklancer,SQL Injection Vulnerability,High Risk Vulnerability,Plugin Detection
summary: 该插件用于检测Quicklancer应用是否存在SQL注入漏洞，通过构造特定请求并测量响应时间来判断漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the Quicklancer application has SQL injection vulnerabilities. It determines the existence of vulnerabilities by constructing specific requests and measuring response time.
